com.ibm.disni.verbs

类 IbvRecvWR

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.disni.verbs.IbvRecvWR
  • 直接已知子类:
    NatIbvRecvWR

    public class IbvRecvWR
extends Object
    Represent a receive work request. Applications create work request and post them onto queue pairs for execution. Each work request is composed of several scatter/gather elements, each of which referring to one single buffer.
